ologies and variability are inconsistent with a scaled-up T Tauri MA\nscenario. We suggest that as magnetic field structure and strength change\ndramatically with increasing stellar mass from T Tauri to Herbig Ae/Be stars,\nso too may accretion and outflow processes.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 31 Oct 2017 04:30:11 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Tue, 12 Dec 2017 16:27:50 GMT"}],"update_date":"2017-12-13"}
