with their products being pure contractions are\nunitarily equivalent if and only if their characteristic triples coincide. We\nalso characterize triples which qualify as the characteristic triple for some\npair $(T_1,T_2)$ of commuting contractions such that $T_1T_2$ is a pure\ncontraction.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 31 Oct 2017 08:20:52 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Sun, 21 Jan 2018 02:37:48 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Thu, 15 Feb 2018 03:13:27 GMT"},{"version":"v4","created":"Thu, 22 Mar 2018 04:05:02 GMT"}],"update_date":"2018-03-23"}
